 which would be too expensive.
 Rather,
 we compute 
\begin_inset Formula $\mm^{-1}b$
\end_inset

 as needed by using the previously computed 
\begin_inset Formula $\mm^{-1}$
\end_inset

 (from possibly many iterations ago) with the maintained low-rank Woodbury update.
\end_layout

